check if a move is legal
 - check if a piece is findable (enough disambiguation was provided)
 - check if the move is possible
    - check if the piece can move there (that piece can physically get there)
    - check if the path there is not blocked (for sliding pieces)
    - check if the destination square isnt bloked by your own piece
    - check if it doesnt leave your king for capture

other chess stuff
